                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6980" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0474</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8161 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">别走！新生代知识型人才！——Guardian公司雇佣关系重塑之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The way to rebuild Guardian employment relationship</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙莹，赵高闻璐，李松岩</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京佳安卫康科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科研、咨询业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新生代；知识型员工；离职；雇佣关系</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">New generation; Knowledge Worker; Resign; Employment Relationship</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着新时代的到来，新生代员工逐渐成为劳动力大部队的主力军，教育资源供给的不断扩大也让接受过高等教育的新生代员工逐年增加，他们就是新生代知识型员工。本案例讲述了Guardian公司创立至今，由人才离职问题引发的关于雇佣关系重塑的思考。案例以雇佣关系为基础，描述了Guardian公司针对新生代知识型员工的个性特点，制定的一系列卓有成效的改革措施，包括改善薪资结构、优化工作流程、改善工作环境、提出轮岗制度、加强培训和沟通等。本案例专注于雇佣关系相关理论知识，涵盖了雇佣关系的定义、内涵、分类、转化路径以及和谐雇佣关系的构建路径等内容。从Guardian公司这一基因检测民营初创企业的角度出发，展现了新时代民营初创企业与新生代知识型员工在自身发展与互相促进之中面临的矛盾与挑战。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> With the arrival of the new era, the new generation of employees has gradually become the main force of the labor force. The continuous expansion of the supply of educational resources has also made the new generation of employees who have received higher education increase year by year. They are the new generation of knowledge workers. This case describes Guardian company founded so far, caused by the problem of talent turnover on employment relationship remodeling thinking. Based on the employment relationship, the case describes a series of effective reform measures formulated by Guardian Company for the personality characteristics of the new generation of knowledge workers, including improving salary structure, optimizing workflow, improving working environment, proposing rotation system, strengthening training and communication. This case focuses on the theoretical knowledge of employment relations, covering the definition, connotation, classification, transformation path and the construction path of harmonious employment relations. From the perspective of Guardian company, a gene detection private start-up, this paper shows the contradictions and challenges faced by private start-ups in the new era and the new generation of knowledge workers in their development and mutual promotion.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雇佣关系的定义；不同类型的雇佣关系模型；不同类型雇佣关系对比与选择；雇佣关系对企业和员工的影响；雇佣关系的优化；构建和谐雇佣关系的路径</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
